<DIV>
<TABLE height=3D626 cellSpacing=3D0 cellPadding=3D0 width=3D383 =
vspace=3D"0" hspace=3D"0">
  <TBODY>
  <TR>
    <TD=20
    style=3D"PADDING-RIGHT: 0in; PADDING-LEFT: 0in; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0in; =
PADDING-TOP: 0in"=20
    vAlign=3Dtop align=3Dleft height=3D626>
      <P class=3DStyle6 style=3D"MARGIN: 0in 0.05pt 0pt 4.8pt"><SPAN=20
      style=3D"FONT-FAMILY: Times-Roman">48 </SPAN><I><SPAN=20
      style=3D"FONT-FAMILY: Times-Italic">The Blind Watchmaker =
</SPAN></I><I><SPAN=20
      style=3D"FONT-FAMILY: Times-Roman"><BR><BR></SPAN></I></P>
      <P class=3DStyle4 style=3D"MARGIN-LEFT: 4.3pt"><SPAN=20
      style=3D"FONT-FAMILY: Times-Roman">WEASEL. In this instance the =
winning=20
      phrase of the next 'generation' happened to be: </SPAN></P>
      <P class=3DStyle4 style=3D"MARGIN: 0in 93.2pt 0pt 14.15pt"><SPAN=20
      style=3D"FONT-FAMILY: Times-Roman">WDLTMNLT DTJBSWIRZREZLMQCO P =
</SPAN></P>
      <P class=3DStyle4=20
      style=3D"MARGIN: 0in 0.75pt 0pt 3.85pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0.25pt; =
LINE-HEIGHT: 10.55pt"><SPAN=20
      style=3D"FONT-FAMILY: Times-Roman">Not an obvious improvement! But =
the=20
      procedure is repeated, again mutant 'progeny' are 'bred from' the =
phrase,=20
      and a new 'winner' is chosen. This goes on, generation after =
generation.=20
      After 10 generations, the phrase chosen for 'breeding' was: =
</SPAN></P>
      <P class=3DStyle4 style=3D"MARGIN: 0in 101.1pt 0pt 13.2pt"><SPAN=20
      style=3D"FONT-FAMILY: Times-Roman">MDLDMNLS ITpSWHRZREZ MECS P =
</SPAN></P>
      <P class=3DStyle4 style=3D"MARGIN: 0in 162.8pt 0pt 3.1pt"><SPAN=20
      style=3D"FONT-FAMILY: Times-Roman">After 20 generations it was: =
</SPAN></P>
      <P class=3DStyle4 style=3D"MARGIN: 0in 110.1pt 0pt 12.7pt"><SPAN=20
      style=3D"FONT-FAMILY: Times-Roman">MELDINLS IT ISWPRKE Z WECSEL =
</SPAN></P>
      <P class=3DStyle5 style=3D"MARGIN: 0in 2.35pt 0pt 2.65pt"><B><SPAN =

      style=3D"FONT-FAMILY: Times-Bold">By </SPAN></B><SPAN=20
      style=3D"FONT-FAMILY: Times-Roman">now, the eye of faith fancies =
that it=20
      </SPAN><B><SPAN style=3D"FONT-FAMILY: Times-Bold">can =
</SPAN></B><SPAN=20
      style=3D"FONT-FAMILY: Times-Roman">see </SPAN><B><SPAN=20
      style=3D"FONT-FAMILY: Times-Bold">a resemblance to the =
</SPAN></B></P>
      <P class=3DStyle5 style=3D"MARGIN: 0in 57.2pt 0pt 2.9pt"><SPAN=20
      style=3D"FONT-FAMILY: Times-Roman">target phrase. By 30 =
generations there=20
      can be </SPAN><B><SPAN style=3D"FONT-FAMILY: Times-Bold">no doubt: =

      </SPAN></B></P>
      <P class=3DStyle4 style=3D"MARGIN: 0in 112.05pt 0pt 12.5pt"><SPAN=20
      style=3D"FONT-FAMILY: Times-Roman">METHINGS IT ISWLIKE B WECSEL =
</SPAN></P>
      <P class=3DStyle4 style=3D"MARGIN: 0in 49.3pt 0pt 2.4pt"><SPAN=20
      style=3D"FONT-FAMILY: Times-Roman">Generation 40 takes us to =
within one=20
      letter of the target: </SPAN></P>
      <P class=3DStyle4 style=3D"MARGIN: 0in 119.5pt 0pt 12pt"><SPAN=20
      style=3D"FONT-FAMILY: Times-Roman">METHINKS IT IS LIKE I WEASEL =
</SPAN></P>
      <P class=3DStyle4 style=3D"MARGIN: 0in 4pt 0pt 1.7pt"><SPAN=20
      style=3D"FONT-FAMILY: Times-Roman">And the target was finally =
reached in=20
      generation 43. A second run of the computer began with the phrase: =

      </SPAN></P>
      <P class=3DStyle4 style=3D"MARGIN: 0in 78.55pt 0pt 11.5pt"><SPAN=20
      style=3D"FONT-FAMILY: Times-Roman">Y YVMQKZPFfXWVHGLAWFVCHQXYOPY,=20
</SPAN></P>
      <P class=3DStyle4 style=3D"MARGIN: 0in 35.85pt 0pt 1.45pt"><SPAN=20
      style=3D"FONT-FAMILY: Times-Roman">passed through (again reporting =
only=20
      every tenth generation): </SPAN></P>
      <P class=3DStyle4=20
      style=3D"MARGIN: 0in 102.9pt 0pt 11.3pt; TEXT-INDENT: 0.25pt; =
LINE-HEIGHT: 10.65pt"><SPAN=20
      style=3D"FONT-FAMILY: Times-Roman">Y YVMQKSPFTXWSHLIKEFV HQYSPY=20
      YETHINKSPITXISHLIKEFA WQYSEY METHINKS IT ISSLIKE A WEFSEY METHINKS =
IT=20
      ISBLIKE A WEASES METHINKS IT ISJLIKE A WEASEO METHINKS IT IS LIKE =
A WEASEP=20
      </SPAN></P>
      <P class=3DStyle4 style=3D"MARGIN: 0in 4.45pt 0pt 0.5pt"><SPAN=20
      style=3D"FONT-FAMILY: Times-Roman">and reached the target phrase =
in=20
      generation </SPAN><B><SPAN style=3D"FONT-FAMILY: Times-Bold">64. m =
a=20
      </SPAN></B><SPAN style=3D"FONT-FAMILY: Times-Roman">third run the =
computer=20
      started with: </SPAN></P>
      <P class=3DStyle4 style=3D"MARGIN: 0in 89.05pt 0pt 10.3pt"><SPAN=20
      style=3D"FONT-FAMILY: Times-Roman">GEWRGZRPBCTPGQMCKHFDBGW ZCCF =
</SPAN></P>
      <P class=3DStyle4 style=3D"MARGIN: 0in 5.4pt 0pt 0.5pt"><SPAN=20
      style=3D"FONT-FAMILY: Times-Roman">and reached METHINKS IT IS LIKE =
A WEASEL=20
      in 41 generations of selective 'breeding'. </SPAN></P>
      <P class=3DStyle4=20
      style=3D"TEXT-INDENT: 10.1pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 10.7pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: =
4.95pt"><SPAN=20
      style=3D"FONT-FAMILY: Times-Roman">The exact time taken by the =
computer to=20
      reach the target doesn't matter. If you want to know, it completed =
the=20
      whole exercise for me, the first time, while I was out to lunch. =
It took=20
      about half an hour. (Computer enthusiasts may think this unduly =
slow. The=20
      reason is that </SPAN></P>
      <P class=3DStyle4=20
      style=3D"TEXT-INDENT: 10.1pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 10.7pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: =
4.95pt"><SPAN=20
      style=3D"COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: =
Times-Roman"></SPAN>&nbsp;</P></TD></TR></TBODY></TABLE></DIV><BR=20
clear=3Dall>
