    vAlign=3Dtop align=3Dleft height=3D206>
      <P class=3DStyle18 style=3D"MARGIN-RIGHT: 0.4pt"><B><SPAN=20
      style=3D"FONT-FAMILY: Helvetica-Bold">326 </SPAN></B><I><SPAN=20
      style=3D"FONT-FAMILY: Times-Italic">Bibliography =
</SPAN><BR><BR></I></P>
      <P class=3DStyle19 style=3D"MARGIN-LEFT: 0.25pt">87. Van Valen, L. =
(1973| A=20
      new evolutionary law. <I><SPAN=20
