      <P class=3DStyle19 style=3D"MARGIN-LEFT: 0.5pt">89. Williams, G. =
C. (1966)=20
      <I><SPAN style=3D"FONT-FAMILY: Times-Italic">Adaptation and =
Natural=20
      Selection. </SPAN></I>New Jersey: Princeton University Press. </P>
      <P class=3DStyle19 style=3D"MARGIN-RIGHT: 0.5pt">90. Wilson, E. 0. =
(1971)=20
      <I><SPAN style=3D"FONT-FAMILY: Times-Italic">The Insect Societies. =

