      <P class=3DStyle19 style=3D"MARGIN-RIGHT: 0.15pt">91. Wilson, E. =
0. (1984)=20
      <I><SPAN style=3D"FONT-FAMILY: Times-Italic">Biophilia.=20
      </SPAN></I>Cambridge, Mass: Harvard University Press </P>
      <P class=3DStyle19 style=3D"MARGIN: 0in 8.75pt 0pt 0.25pt">92. =
Young, <I><SPAN=20
      style=3D"FONT-FAMILY: Times-Italic">]. </SPAN></I>Z. (1950) =
<I><SPAN=20
      style=3D"FONT-FAMILY: Times-Italic">The Life of Vertebrates.=20
      </SPAN></I>Oxford: Clarendon Press. </P>
      <P class=3DStyle19 style=3D"MARGIN: 0in 8.75pt 0pt 0.25pt"><SPAN=20
      style=3D"COLOR: =
black"></SPAN>&nbsp;</P></TD></TR></TBODY></TABLE></DIV><BR=20
